11 September 2019 Government will launch the District Based Service Delivery Model on 17 September 2019 at Zalu Hill Sports field, Ingquza Hill Local Municipality, Lusikisiki, Eastern Cape. Members of the media who wish to cover the launch are requested to apply for accreditation by filing in the attached registration form and send their details to Takalani Mukwevho on takalanim@gcis.gov.za or Ndyebo Kopo on ndyebok@gcis.gov.za, all fields must be completed. The deadline for the submission of the details is Friday, 13 September 2019 at 12h00. The details for collection of media accreditation cards will be communicated in due course. For more information regarding accreditation please contact:Mr Ndlelantle Pinyana Cell: 076 142 8606E-mail: ndlelantle@gcis.gov.za Terence ManaseCell: 082 338 6707E-mail: Terrence@presidency.gov.za